==Type IXC/40==
Type IXC/40 was an improved Type IXC with slightly increased range and surfaced speed. is on display at Woodside Ferry Terminal, Birkenhead.

===List of Type IXC/40 submarines===
DeSchiMAG AG Weser and Seebeckwerft of Bremen, and Deutsche Werft of Hamburg, built 87 of this type.
